1
00:00:00,570 --> 00:00:03,520
The Cage of Love

2
00:00:03,520 --> 00:00:06,110
<i>Episode 19</i>

3
00:00:08,110 --> 00:00:12,250
If it wasn't for your help, I wouldn't have been able to leave unscathed.

4
00:00:12,250 --> 00:00:16,920
Am I that great? I'm only just your subordinate who runs around doing errands.

5
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:20,000
I just act according to you instructions.

6
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:41,020
But

7
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:44,680
did you really kill Wu Hong Da?

8
00:00:44,680 --> 00:00:47,250
Of course not.

9
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:49,680
Why are you so nervous then?

10
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:54,600
Don't worry. Even if you killed someone,

11
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:57,420
I wouldn't tell anyone.

12
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,370
I really didn't kill anyone.

13
00:01:03,350 --> 00:01:08,080
I still suspect that Jiang Yu killed Wu Hong Da.

14
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:14,110
He had the motive to kill, intent to commit the crime, and owns an identical pen.

15
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:20,200
In order to mask the truth, he has done some dirty deeds against me.

16
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:25,920
By doing that, he sabotaged my love with Cai Hong.

17
00:01:29,950 --> 00:01:34,700
Forget it. If you are fighting in the business arena,

18
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:39,670
one can lose their head and commit murder.

19
00:01:39,670 --> 00:01:41,960
This is too scary.

20
00:01:43,990 --> 00:01:48,390
You are too ethical.

21
00:01:48,390 --> 00:01:51,720
How could you let Jiang Yu bully you again?

22
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:55,390
If this drags on, there will come a day when you will suffer.

23
00:01:55,390 --> 00:01:57,090
I'm waiting for the opportunity now.

24
00:01:58,370 --> 00:01:59,900
When the opportunity is here,

25
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:02,190
he won't be able to get away.

26
00:02:03,750 --> 00:02:09,020
From what I can see, Jiang Yu and you are playing games with each other.

27
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:14,370
Can't even help oneself.

28
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:18,250
Okay.

29
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:20,090
Don't be too harsh on yourself.

30
00:02:48,510 --> 00:02:52,950
Cai Hong. You haven't eaten anything for the whole day. Eat something.

31
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:01,150
Mrs Li. I'm really not hungry.

32
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:03,130
Eat something.

33
00:03:03,130 --> 00:03:07,270
Young Master already said that if you don't eat anything, I'm not doing a good job.

34
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:12,190
I have to change and redo things until you eat.

35
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:14,500
Help me please.

36
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:18,550
I will eat then, Mrs Li.

37
00:03:21,810 --> 00:03:24,760
Frankly, Young Master is doing this for your own good.

38
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:29,170
I don't know what the others think but I can

39
00:03:29,170 --> 00:03:32,320
see clearly.

40
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:35,610
You don't need to twist it. Just eat it.

41
00:03:38,830 --> 00:03:40,920
This is right.

42
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:07,030
Brother.

43
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:15,980
What do you take Wu Cai Hong as?

44
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:21,890
What do you mean? Of course, she is a servant.

45
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:28,580
But your attitude to her, is that of a servant?

46
00:04:28,580 --> 00:04:31,280
I treat all my servants equally.

47
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,240
You are lying.

48
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:37,150
Would you take a servant to view the lotus pond?

49
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:40,570
Would you be concerned that your servant is not eating?

50
00:04:40,570 --> 00:04:42,240
Brother, don't forget, she is Wu Hong Da's daughter.

51
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:46,190
I'm not a three year old kid. I don't need you to tell me what to do.

52
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:50,440
You know that I didn't say anything wrong.

53
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:54,650
You are angry because you have a guilty conscious.

54
00:04:54,650 --> 00:04:56,700
What I said was right.

55
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:59,900
Your feelings towards Wu Cai Hong already surpasses that of an ordinary person.

56
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,920
Leave.

57
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,090
I can leave

58
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:09,520
but I would still like to advise you.

59
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:14,380
Don't let your personal feelings get in the way.

60
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:43,660
Did you see how Young Master treats Wu Cai Hong better than anyone?

61
00:05:43,660 --> 00:05:47,880
Based on what you said, Wu Cai Hong is the young mistress.

62
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:50,920
We should treat her better in the future then.

63
00:05:52,030 --> 00:05:57,360
If Wu Cai Hong becomes his wife, what will happen to us?

64
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:59,450
They may be childhood friends

65
00:05:59,450 --> 00:06:02,640
but Miss has feelings for Young Master who is not interested.

66
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:07,900
But Miss's affections towards Master are unintentional. She lights up every time she see's him.

67
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:11,440
No wonder Miss hates Wu Cai Hong so much.

68
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:16,580
Even though they address her as the mistress of the house, her family name is Fang not Jiang.

69
00:06:16,580 --> 00:06:19,570
She is also an outsider.

70
00:06:19,570 --> 00:06:26,930
If she can't be the Young Master's wife, she will have to marry someone and leave the house sooner or later.

71
00:06:26,930 --> 00:06:31,750
If a girl wants to marry, she should marry an authentic Young Master.

72
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:36,330
Look. Miss has placed so many thoughts on Young Master.

73
00:06:36,330 --> 00:06:40,140
It was really rotten and a waste of time.

74
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:42,400
That's right.

75
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:45,380
<i>I will never leave this family.</i>

76
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:48,530
<i>I will also never leave Mom and Brother.</i>

77
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:53,430
<i>Wu Cai Hong. I won't let you and Brother be together.</i>

78
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:13,570
Miss Fang. Are you really inviting me out for tea? It can't be that simple.

79
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:16,810
I have already thought it through. I can help you.

80
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:22,030
You are not only helping me but yourself too.

81
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:27,760
Say whatever you want but let me state this first. I can help you

82
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:30,100
but you must never harm my brother.

83
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:35,320
I must not harm your brother?

84
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:39,450
But you have harmed Cai Hong a couple of times. What does this count?

85
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:44,910
Looks like you are not sincere in collaborating with me.

86
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:50,410
Miss Fang, let me advise you. You don't have much time.

87
00:07:50,410 --> 00:07:55,380
If you don't manage it, I'm afraid that when Cai Hong enters the Jiang family

88
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:57,480
and becomes your sister-in-law,

89
00:08:00,330 --> 00:08:04,030
what I would lose is just Cai Hong.

90
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:07,630
What you will lose is not only Jiang Yu.

91
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,900
Are you threatening me now?

92
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:14,370
Why would I collaborate with a menacing person?

93
00:08:14,370 --> 00:08:18,730
Once a friend becomes an enemy, he becomes more dangerous than the enemy.

94
00:08:18,730 --> 00:08:23,380
Yet once an enemy becomes a friend, he will be more reliable than a friend.

95
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:26,040
By helping me, you are helping yourself too.

96
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,620
Fine. How can I help you then?

97
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:33,110
Get the slave contract for me as soon as possible.

98
00:08:33,110 --> 00:08:36,280
If I could do this, would I still be here?

99
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,570
I believe you will find the way.

100
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:41,440
I will wait for your news.

101
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:47,060
How was the investigation regarding the opium case at Ling Long?

102
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:53,320
There was a lead but the investigation midway, stopped.

103
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:59,420
We found the court official who handled this case twelve years ago but when we went to visit him,

104
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:04,360
he refused to reveal anything about that night.

105
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:17,020
He refused to talk? This means there was a major problem in the case.

106
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:22,820
Yes, I find it strange too. This court official is on extremely good terms with Jiang Wen Yuan.

107
00:09:22,820 --> 00:09:28,530
Since Master Jiang's death, the top investigators have all left.

108
00:09:28,530 --> 00:09:31,920
Thus, I feel that he knows some insider's information.

109
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:47,560
Please.

110
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:50,230
Please wait.

111
00:09:50,230 --> 00:09:52,760
Old Master. Boss Zhou is here.

112
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:56,170
Leave.

113
00:09:56,170 --> 00:09:59,820
If you are here to find out about the Ling Long case,

114
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:03,030
sorry, please go back.

115
00:10:04,530 --> 00:10:09,810
Uncle Gao. I'm here to seek advice regarding the Ling Long case from twelve years ago.

116
00:10:09,810 --> 00:10:14,730
At the same time, I'm also here to visit my mother's foe.

117
00:10:14,730 --> 00:10:18,890
Do you still remember, three years ago, the aunt from the weaving and dyeing factory.

118
00:10:22,190 --> 00:10:25,770
Are you referring to her husband, Zhou Da Liang who had lung disease?

119
00:10:25,770 --> 00:10:29,330
I'm his son, Zhou Shao Tian.

120
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:44,680
Talking about this, you look exactly like your mother.

121
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:49,510
Uncle Gao. I visited you without advance notice today.

122
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:52,000
You definitely must have a request.

123
00:10:53,730 --> 00:11:01,690
I know that you don't want to talk about it but I still would like to find out about the opium case at Ling Long.

124
00:11:01,690 --> 00:11:05,720
Please do me a small favour.

125
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:09,360
Wasn't the case settled then?

126
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:12,180
It has been such a long time and that person has already died.

127
00:11:12,180 --> 00:11:14,970
Why do you still want to talk about it?

128
00:11:14,970 --> 00:11:19,430
If it weren't for my mother's wish, I wouldn't want to talk about this either.

129
00:11:19,430 --> 00:11:21,180
Your mother's wish?

130
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:23,380
When my father got sick and was lying in bed,

131
00:11:23,380 --> 00:11:25,870
Old Master Jiang took care of my mother.

132
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:29,810
He gave her some of Ling Long's business. Old Master Jiang knew about my family's hardship.

133
00:11:29,810 --> 00:11:34,010
He gave wage advances to try to solve the urgent needs of my family.

134
00:11:34,010 --> 00:11:37,120
If it weren't for Old Master Jiang's kindness,

135
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:41,980
I'm afraid that my mom wouldn't have been able to support me and her sick husband.

136
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:47,520
Boss Jiang was really a good person.

137
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:51,910
When Boss Jiang passed away, my mother has never talked bad about him.

138
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:57,950
She said that someone like Old Master Jiang would never use opium to frame anyone.

139
00:11:57,950 --> 00:12:02,730
Unfortunately with our family situation the way it was, Jiang was unable to be compensated.

140
00:12:02,730 --> 00:12:06,860
Only during the Winter Solstice Festival, his burning point for money was all for nothing.

141
00:12:08,390 --> 00:12:13,760
Now with mixed effort, Old Jiang can rest in peace.

142
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:17,160
I couldn't pay him for his kindness to my family.

143
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:21,990
The only thing I can do is to prove Boss Jiang's innocence.

144
00:12:21,990 --> 00:12:25,410
He will then rest in peace in heaven.

145
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:34,580
Your mother has such a son who is willing to redeem himself for the family,

146
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:37,440
that is her good fortune.

147
00:12:38,770 --> 00:12:43,770
But the case happened twelve years ago, it won't be easy to turn around the case.

148
00:12:43,770 --> 00:12:49,390
I have no choice but to seek your help now.

149
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:54,580
I won't be able to help you

150
00:12:55,770 --> 00:12:59,910
but there are some matters that I can tell you.

151
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:05,500
Old Master Jiang and I were on very good terms. I know how he was too.

152
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:07,720
Just like what you said,

153
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:12,940
he would never do anything like that.

154
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:20,550
The years following the wrongful death of Boss Jiang, there were a lot of people who could have cried foul.

155
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:27,010
The strange thing is that he payed for other's grievances but everyone suffered in the end.

156
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:33,680
I'm ashamed for not speaking sooner but now I can help prove Jiang's innocence.

157
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:40,510
But I think when he was implicated and everyone was tight-lipped.

158
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:46,840
I wanted to find a home for windows and orphans and find a solution

159
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:53,340
but when I heard that they were kicked out by the tribe, they have been hiding in their hometown.

160
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:59,400
I sent men to find out about their whereabouts but there was no news.

161
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:04,330
I heard that Jiang Yu is very capable now and he has gotten back Ling Long.

162
00:14:04,330 --> 00:14:10,070
At that time, I was a coward and didn't dare to speak up on his father's behalf.

163
00:14:10,070 --> 00:14:15,990
I don't have the face to see him. Thus, I have never visited him.

164
00:14:15,990 --> 00:14:21,050
If you are sure that Old Master Jiang was duped, where is the evidence?

165
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:28,100
The incident happened a long time ago. If there are any evidence, it would already have been burnt.

166
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:32,670
Boss Jiang was wronged and not only be my side of the story.

167
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:40,310
I think if you could find the case file from that year, perhaps you could read through the documents.

