169
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:02,790
- Miss Lu.
- You are looking for me?

170
00:16:02,790 --> 00:16:07,550
I'm here to ask for your help to investigate a case.

171
00:16:07,550 --> 00:16:09,540
You are really insincere.

172
00:16:11,370 --> 00:16:15,160
When you look for me, it's either to help you find a fountain pen or to investigate a case.

173
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:19,380
Can't you treat me to a meal or go to the movies?

174
00:16:19,380 --> 00:16:24,380
As for dinner and movie thing, how could I dare to cross warlord Lu?

175
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:28,990
We are discussing business and nothing else.

176
00:16:30,580 --> 00:16:33,550
Speak. What help do you need?

177
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:40,550
During the Xuantong years is when the opium trafficking case took place.

178
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:45,160
We are a republic country now and you want me to help you investigate an official court case?

179
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:47,540
On what ground do you think I am able to do that?

180
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:50,750
If you cannot do it, Miss Lu, no one can.

181
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:55,940
I would like to see the records of the case. You are the only one who can help me with this.

182
00:16:57,540 --> 00:16:59,130
Fine.

183
00:16:59,130 --> 00:17:04,990
Since you said that we are presently discussing business now and nothing else,

184
00:17:06,040 --> 00:17:08,830
if I can help you with this difficult request,

185
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:11,190
how are you going to thank me?

186
00:17:12,490 --> 00:17:14,590
Tell me.

187
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:20,280
I want Ling Long's secret formula.

188
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:25,080
I think you are mistaken. I was with Ling Long for many years and have never heard about this.

189
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:30,320
I know that you don't have it. Anyway, it's not that urgent just as long as you will help me.

190
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:34,710
When doing business, it's for mutual benefits. Please do something for me.

191
00:17:34,710 --> 00:17:39,950
If you think that you can't do it, let's not transact this business then.

192
00:17:48,730 --> 00:17:50,780
I agree.

193
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:55,440
Don't play me. I know many secrets about you.

194
00:17:56,250 --> 00:17:58,020
I'm leaving.

195
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:23,870
<i>Cai Hong, be patient. I will come and get you soon.</i>

196
00:18:23,870 --> 00:18:30,140
<i>I will be able to show Jiang Yu's true colour soon and reveal the truth for you.</i>

197
00:18:37,090 --> 00:18:38,470
Is everyone here?

198
00:18:38,470 --> 00:18:40,400
Yes.

199
00:18:41,300 --> 00:18:47,470
Today is the 15th of July, Ghost Festival, and the day for us to remember Old Master.

200
00:18:47,470 --> 00:18:53,350
Mom. I have already prepared everything.

201
00:18:55,980 --> 00:19:03,320
Every year, we have prepared for this festival. There was no other exception.

202
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:08,950
Especially when Old Master will be back today. Everyone, don't delay it.

203
00:19:08,950 --> 00:19:10,860
Yes.

204
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:12,720
Go and do whatever you are assigned to do.

205
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:15,230
Yes.

206
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:16,670
Have you heated up the buns?

207
00:19:16,670 --> 00:19:18,490
Yes, it should be ready soon.

208
00:19:18,490 --> 00:19:20,490
Let me take a look.

209
00:19:22,490 --> 00:19:25,200
Let me take a look. Are you okay?

210
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,750
Let me see.

211
00:19:26,750 --> 00:19:28,600
Move aside.

212
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:31,030
What's wrong?

213
00:19:31,030 --> 00:19:32,800
Did you scald yourself? Are you okay?

214
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:34,240
Let me take a look.

215
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,860
It's not me.

216
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:39,600
It's Miss.

217
00:19:58,050 --> 00:20:01,980
Brother, you still don't admit that you treat Wu Cai Hong differently?

218
00:20:04,330 --> 00:20:08,670
I was flustered just now and didn't check who was hurt.

219
00:20:08,670 --> 00:20:12,720
That's because the problem is you didn't see who was hurt.

220
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:17,160
Your subconscious behavior is being driven by your inner thoughts.

221
00:20:18,650 --> 00:20:22,450
Brother, I'm your sister.

222
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:25,730
We went through hard times for twelve years.

223
00:20:25,730 --> 00:20:29,090
We got back Ling Long together to take revenge for father.

224
00:20:29,090 --> 00:20:34,520
Other than your mother, I'm your closest relative in this world.

225
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:36,370
But why was

226
00:20:36,370 --> 00:20:41,010
the first person that you were concerned about today was Wu Cai Hong and not me?

227
00:20:41,010 --> 00:20:45,490
In your heart, Wu Cai Hong is more valuable than me.

228
00:20:45,490 --> 00:20:47,510
You are still not going to admit it?

229
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:51,910
I have matters to attend to. I'm leaving first.

230
00:20:51,910 --> 00:20:53,700
What you are feeling inside?

231
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:56,080
Why must you force me to talk about this?

232
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:03,560
Fei Fei. What exactly do you want?

233
00:21:03,560 --> 00:21:07,030
I want Wu Cai Hong to leave this house.

234
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:10,210
Since you can't control your own feelings,

235
00:21:10,210 --> 00:21:14,420
don't let your emotions bring you down.

236
00:21:17,940 --> 00:21:22,010
Brother. You won't let me and Mom

237
00:21:22,010 --> 00:21:25,790
and also our father who is in heaven be disappointed with you, right?

238
00:21:25,790 --> 00:21:31,820
I will repeat myself. I will decide my own affairs.

239
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:39,080
Brother, you are really foolish.

240
00:21:39,970 --> 00:21:42,910
Do you think you can run away from this problem?

241
00:21:50,990 --> 00:21:54,150
Come back, dear.

242
00:21:55,770 --> 00:22:01,210
It has been many years. How are you doing in that world?

